                  <additions>
                     <note>Chronogram of Tabrīz earthquake in 1194, "az zilzilah shud kharāb Tabrīz". It should be noted that the chronogram in Abjad letters will refer to the year of 1194 only if we ignore the word "Tabrīz", i.e. it is "az zilzilah shud kharāb" which equals to 1194. This is discussed in "Mavād al-tavārīkh" of the late Ḥusayn Nakhjavānī (printed in Tehran, 1343, page 451).</note>
